divs: Sighting DetailsAt 10 pm when coming back from the store, while turning into my neighborhood I caught a glimpse of something large in the sky. I thought I was imagining it until my friend asked me if I saw it too. It was large and like nothing I have ever seen. Kind of tear drop shaped and it hovered. It was only visible for a couple of minutes and disappeared just as quick as it appeared. We searched our immediate area hoping to see it but with no luck. We did notice increased air traffic in our sky after this happened.
Summary: 2 eyewitnesses saw a large object hovering.
